channel.title: Hugo's nest of thoughts
channel.description: "I hold a MsC from the faculty of Engineering, Lund University. Even though I didn't study computer science this is my new born interest. I work as a developer and I try to take in as much as possible in the field. I am interested in machine-learning and more specifically deep-learning. Python will be my preferred weapon of choice but soon enough I will also be able to wield C++.""
